lead_paragraph: Matt Shoemaker turned his head just enough to avoid taking Kyle Seager's 105 mph line drive square in the face, then stumbled before falling to the infield grass.

headline.print_headline: Shoemaker Has Skull Fracture From Liner, Angels Beat Seattle
